  "title": "Rollover Arrangement",
  "description": "Is an Arrangement to extend or renew an existing financial arrangement at maturity, by continuing the obligation under revised or agreed terms instead of terminating it.\r\n\r\nArrangement stipulating the modalities for an automatic renewal of the agreement\r\n\r\ni.e. the replacement of the agreement with a new one without renewed negociation and witout explicit agreement of the customer \r\n\r\nTerm Deposit Renewal is a feature, in which the bank or financial institution renews a customer's deposit under similar conditions upon maturity or before maturity. In the latter case a penalty for early renewal may apply.",
